				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">First off I have to say, anyone who thinks Everquest is full of content is full of crap! What is there in Everquest? A room with NPC's and your a person there with a sword ready to kill it, then you sit down and wait for it to repop. It's like playing a game for the original NES, there are only 2 outcomes - win or die. There are no guild wars, no sieges, or any PvP except for the highly unbalanced EQ PvP servers. ShadowBane is a revolution in online gaming, all characters can be unique. The player run towns are going to be incredible and just the aspect of going to war and capturing another player city is a gigantic advangtage over EQ. 
